## 🔥 Why This Project Matters

Most SQL projects stop at queries.

**This one goes further → it connects data to business impact.**

* 📈 Identify revenue drivers
* 🎯 Optimize marketing channels
* ⚠️ Detect financial risks
* 👥 Evaluate sales performance

---

## 📌 Project Overview

A **real-world SQL analytics project** simulating an IT company’s sales ecosystem.

It transforms raw transactional data into **insights that decision-makers can act on.**

---

## 💡 Key Insights (Business Impact)

<div align="center">

| Insight                              | Impact                       |
| ------------------------------------ | ---------------------------- |
| 📈 65% revenue from repeat customers | Focus on retention           |
| 🎯 Referrals outperform LinkedIn 3X  | Reallocate marketing budget  |
| ⚠️ ₹2.3 Cr unpaid orders             | Improve collections strategy |
| 📉 Bottom 20% → only 8% revenue      | Sales team optimization      |

</div>

