## 🧩 Dataset Architecture

```text
Customers ──┐
            ├── Sales_Orders ── Order_Details ── Products
Employees ──┘
            └── Payments

Leads (Marketing Funnel)
```

---

## 🔍 SQL Skills Demonstrated

* 🧠 Advanced JOINs (multi-table analysis)
* 📊 Window Functions (RANK, NTILE, ROW_NUMBER)
* 🔁 CTEs & Subqueries
* 📈 KPI Calculations
* 📉 Trend Analysis

---

## 🧪 Sample Query

```sql
SELECT 
    CustomerID,
    SUM(TotalAmount) AS Revenue,
    RANK() OVER (ORDER BY SUM(TotalAmount) DESC) AS Rank
FROM Sales_Orders
GROUP BY CustomerID;
```

